dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Yorba Linda and Prado Dam quadrangles (eastern Puente Hills), Los Angeles, Orange, San Bernardino and Riverside Counties, California
dct_alternative_sm: Yorba Linda and Prado Dam quadrangles
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr.; edited by Helmut E. Ehrenspeck.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Prepared in cooperation with the California Dept. of Conservation, Division of Mines and Geology; and the U.S. Geological Survey."
Includes 2 col. cross-sections, location map, and index to sources of geology.
On verso: "Alfred Oswald Woodford" by Dorothy Lalonde Stout, reprinted from California Geology, May 1989, p. 109-112, and port.
dct_creator_sm: California, Division of Mines and Geology.
